                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1468" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1468" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1468" type="surname" value="RESTIEAUX"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1468" type="given" value="JOHN JAMES"></interp>JOHN JAMES RESTIEAUX</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 49.) I saw the prisoner in George-street, St. Giles, on Saturday night, the 10th of June, about half-past eight o'clock, with this bacon under his coat—I asked how he came by it—he threw it down, and said he bought it of a strange man in Holborn—I asked him how much it weighed—he said nine pounds—I took him to the station, and found it weighed ten pounds—he was not drunk.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1469" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1469" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1469" type="surname" value="DUNT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1469" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN DUNT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of John Hutley, a cheesemonger, in Broad-street, St. Giles. On Saturday night I saw the prisoner take hold of this piece of bacon—I asked him if he would buy it—he made no answer—I was busy with several people, and did not miss it till a quarter of an hour after, when the policeman came.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> A man offered to sell it me cheap; he said there was nine pounds of it, and he wanted 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. a pound for it; he said he had got it from a chandler's-shop; I gave him 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. for it, and when the policeman came I dropped it accidentally—I was intoxicated.</p>
